description: Excellent Investment opportunity off Thomas Park. This large-scale three-family has 14 rooms, including 6 bedrooms over 4 levels, and is situated on an oversized lot (2,550) that is ideal for expansion. There is a sub-basement below the 1st living level. The current rents generate $112,800 in gross yearly rent, but the market rents should gross $127,200/Year.  Three solid rental units need only lite cosmetics. Conveniently located near Caron Beach and the Bayview (#11) bus route, and just minutes to Perkins Square and the Broadway Shops & restaurants.
